## Population Rules

Trigger: after every `/retrospective` or `/close-feature`.

| Observation | Target section |
|---|---|
| Domain convention that surprised the team | Domain Conventions |
| Architectural decision affecting future features | Architectural Decisions |
| Code pattern/anti-pattern found in review | Coding Conventions |
| Bug class caught by QA/reviewer | Known Failure Modes |
| Deployment lesson | DevOps Patterns |

Do NOT add: one-time fixes, decisions already in ADRs (link instead), content belonging in code comments/README.
Quality bar: each entry must change a future agent's behavior — if it can't, skip it.
